2025-01-29.title: ASML CEO Says DeepSeek’s Emergence Is ‘Good News’ for AI
2025-01-29.description: ASML Holding NV’s leader brushed off concerns about the artificial intelligence-driven demand for its chipmaking machines after Chinese startup DeepSeek’s low-cost chatbot roiled markets earlier in the week.

2025-01-24.title: ASML Outlook Clouded by Intel, Samsung and China Chip Challenges
2025-01-24.description: After sending shockwaves through the semiconductor industry following a third-quarter earnings miss, scrutiny is building ahead of ASML Holding NV’s results next week with uncertainty over the spending plans of its top clients.

2025-01-27.title: Nvidia, ASML Plunge as DeepSeek Triggers Tech Stock Selloff
2025-01-27.description: Nvidia Corp. and ASML Holding NV shares plunged early Monday as Chinese artificial intelligence startup DeepSeek appeared to provide comparable performance to Western chatbots at a fraction of the price.

2025-01-27.title: ASML Earnings Are Make-or-Break for Europe’s Rally in Key Week
2025-01-27.description: As European stocks stumble from an all-time peak, the stakes are high for corporate earnings from a slate of industry bellwethers including ASML Holding NV this week to revive the rally.
